居屋 夾屋 佢地都唔會有錢買"},{"pid":"9f5a2b6a519e3f5a8904a384dff5d0b2a6677c4c","tid":144210,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:57:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n其實香港新起個啲公屋都唔差<br />\n係細新加坡好多姐</blockquote><br />\n人地疏好多矮好多 仲望到成片天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd綠化又正</blockquote><br />\n呢個的確係<br />\n人地新加坡可發展既地多過香港<br />\n人口又少過香港<br />\n起樓都唔洗起咁細咁密啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以香港個問題唔淨止係房屋政策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n所以我上面咪語開發新界地、郊地、填海黎配合我上面提意既房屋政策囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n郁乜鬼新界佬，政府做得上去既人都係有新界佬係後面撐腰。<br />\n<br />\n人地俾票你先有得做，你點郁到啲新界佬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以就係話睇佢地想唔想搞好香港囉<br />\n究竟係為個人利益定係香港人既利益定係新界佬既利益<br />\n<br />\nBtw 班新界佬惡撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2648f3c579c6acfee8e66df149f44fc0bdbe88ad","tid":144210,"uid":72368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:59:29.000Z","msg":"香港連估算未來人口都做唔到<br />\n搞咩政策都係哂氣"},{"pid":"648d9867a8d8a2fffb404a9f1a95fa811243219b","tid":144210,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:03:25.000Z","msg":"新加坡咁多實業<br />\n香港突然小左地產依條路就乜都無架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7674f4dcef9d3e5efe2d6af05fdbafc76e414cc","tid":144210,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:04:39.000Z","msg":"點解你會覺得佢做唔到或者唔識做？<br />\n佢地係為左地產商同有錢人（揸住好多樓嗰d，包括高官自己）所以先唔敢影響個炒市之嘛<br />\n<br />\n起樓有幾閒唧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a72e727befa9941dfd42d501a181a1f6ae75a